Airtel Tanzania Director of Communications Beatrice Singano said in Dar es Salaam yesterday that Airtel responded and restored immediately the communication services. “Airtel is determined to offer high quality communication services at all year round, during rain and no rain seasons,\[poi to ensure customers continue to use the network as platform and backbone to their economic activities,” she said.For the past one week, several regions in the country have been experiencing a heavy downpour and in some cases have been experiencing floods thus leading to communication breakdown.